snippet.title: SPRiNG FLOWERS new DRESS to iMPRESS!!  Adley & Kensley react to their Salish & Jordan Matter video
snippet.description:
will my Daughter win the $500 challenge from Salish?

JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

HEY EVERYBODY!! Welcome! To a brand new episode of G for Gaming!!! OH YEAH!!
In this week’s episode, Adley, Kensley, and Dad play the new Dress to Impress update!! But first... they’ve gotta watch the brand new Jordan Matter video — I Gave My CREDIT CARD To AGES 1-18!!
Adley and Kensley were in this video!! They went to sooo many fun places and even bought Robux to surprise their family with a PIZZA PARTAY!! You can catch the rest of Adley’s adventure over on A for Adley!!
After the video, it was time to play Dress to Impress.
 First round theme? Holiday clothes!
 But Adley had other plans... She made her own outfit — not with the theme!! So silly!
Then they explored ALL the new Spring Update items — and there’s A LOT!!
 New hairs, new makeups... EVEN NEW WALKS!!
Once they finished checking it all out, they kept playing Dress to Impress until...
 Dad couldn’t take it anymore!!
ANYWAYS — thanks for tuning in to a brand new episode of G FOR GAMING!!!
 THANKS FOR WATCHING!! BYEEEE!!!
 PSSSSHHHHH
